item.title: CVE-2019-5643|2024-09-16T19:14:34.337Z -- computing%20for%20good -- basic%20laboratory%20information%20system
item.description: Computing For Good's Basic Laboratory Information System (also known as C4G BLIS) version 3.5 and earlier suffers from an instance of CWE-284, "Improper Access Control." As a result, an unauthenticated user may enumerate the user names and facility names in use on a particular installation.
